metadata.name: Straws
metadata.description:
Behind the beauty, the sexuality, the excitement, the looks, there is a person behind it all. And it will show itself.
Julia's photos always captivate with their aesthetics and sexuality. By doing this photo shoot we wanted to show how amazing a woman's athletic body looks in an unconventional location in a hay warehouse. The shapes of her body emphasize her sexuality and lightness.
I hope these beautiful photos catch your attention with their energy and ease.
Photo by Andrey Martin (martinslide)
